00:16:12,260 --> 00:16:15,618
Start-up competitions,
business plan contests, etc.,

302
00:16:15,618 --> 00:16:17,182
usually, they are competitive,

303
00:16:17,182 --> 00:16:19,776
you generally get some advice
from the audience

304
00:16:19,776 --> 00:16:21,856
who are your panel of judges or jury

305
00:16:21,856 --> 00:16:24,728
and you can win prize money

306
00:16:24,728 --> 00:16:27,801
which could help fund
the initial stages of a company.

307
00:16:28,791 --> 00:16:33,006
