on the company,

312
00:16:46,263 --> 00:16:48,763
in which case,
the angel group meets regularly

313
00:16:48,763 --> 00:16:52,221
and entrepreneurs make pitches
in front of the angel groups

314
00:16:52,221 --> 00:16:55,908
