325
00:17:28,389 --> 00:17:31,849
and they are definitely interested
in an equity position in the company,

326
00:17:31,849 --> 00:17:34,967
and they would like to see
an exit event happening,

327
00:17:34,967 --> 00:17:39,001
because they raise money
from other people

328
00:17:39,001 --> 00:17:41,151
who are trying to look for investments,

329
00:17:41,151 --> 00:17:44,530
then they take that money
